<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>该班列将转关至阿拉山口口岸后按照</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>TIR（</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>《国际公路车辆运输规定》</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>）</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>模式出境，全程运输里程</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>12000</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>公里。途径哈萨克斯坦</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>-</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>俄罗斯</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>-</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>白俄罗斯</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>-</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>波兰</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>-</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>德国，预计</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>14</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>天后抵达目的地比利时，然后再陆续分发到欧洲其它国家。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
