<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>这是银川跨境电商综试区批复以来，</span></span></span></span></span>银川综保区对内陆9610跨境电商出口货物<span><span><span><span><span>在银川顺利落地的首次探索和初步尝试，今后计划将每天发出3至</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>5</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>辆卡车班列，运输的货物出口至欧洲等地。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
